reviewText: just a guy petting a puppy dicuusing som small information
Just got a Boston puppy and this was a great video.
Not even close to "everything you should know".  Skims important training aspects and leaves out crucial crate training tips.  Very lightweight.  Cute puppy though.
Really rough and kind of youtubey... just not worth the money or the time. What else is there to say
Good introduction for anyone considering getting a Boston Terrior.  The background "music" in the video is obnoxious and dis-tracting. HP Dallas
